msgid ""
"Stripe Crypto payments (USDC) are ONLY available for US-based businesses. If"
" you are outside the US, Stripe will only accept credit card payments to "
"your Stripe balance (not directly to crypto)."
msgstr ""
"Stripe Crypto plaćanja (USDC) dostupna su ISSOLE za tvrtke u SAD-u. Ako se "
"nalazite izvan SAD-a, Stripe će prihvatiti samo plaćanja kreditnom karticom "
"na vaš Stripe saldo (ne izravno na kriptovalutu)."

msgid ""
"If you are in the US, you can use Stripe to receive crypto directly. If "
"outside, consider NOWPayments or CoinGate for direct crypto payouts."
msgstr ""
"Ako se nalazite u SAD-u, možete koristiti Stripe za izravno primanje "
"kriptovaluta. Ako niste, razmislite o NOWPayments ili CoinGate za izravne "
"kripto isplate."

